data.description: A rare five bedroom 3 full bath home sits on 1.95 acre lot with Yerington valley view you DO NOT want to miss out. Property comes with RV hookup and fruit tree. Floor plan is spacious! Kitchen is perfect for lots of homemade cooking and memory building. Schedule your showings today! With a FHA assumable loan at 3.625% interest rate, this home presents a rare opportunity for a qualified buyer. Call listing agent for details. Washer, dryer, refrigerators in laundry rom and security cameras DO NOT convey with property. Trailer out back can be negotiated outside of escrow.
